<i>adverb</i>: 망령되이 [망ː녕뙤이/망ː녕뛔이] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>망령되이 [망ː녕뙤이/망ː녕뛔이]</dt><br>
<dd>irrationally</dd><br>
<dd>늙거나 정신이 흐려져서 말이나 행동이 정상적이지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that words or actions deviate from what is considered normal due to old age or a fuzzy mind.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>